name: Timeless Frida Face 8 - Pleat Clutch
description:
Timeless.... Frida Kahlo will stay.... Frida is a great inspiration to me. She symbolizes strength and beauty.

I made this clutch paying extra attention to the small details. Notice I added delicate flowers to her hair.  This is a Beautiful gift for someone who loves Frida Kahlo dearly. 

Features of this Custom Clutch 

* One of a Kind - Will not be duplicated
* 8 Pleats
* Fully Lined with polka dot fabric
* Pocket Inside
* Strap to wear on your wrist
* Measurements are 10.5"  long 9" tall
* Fully reinforced, durable and not flimsy
* Makes a Great Conversation piece
* No waiting, ready to Ship

"Buy handmade, It's a labor of LOVE"
